{"tid":2488923,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂於台灣成立分公司    疑參考Sony撤離香港做法","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:46:41.000Z","uid":1086,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb42d43a06044ae08aaef8348851160da49533d","tid":2488923,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F2-9.jpg&h=ba4eab91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日任天堂台灣官網作出更新，任天堂香港有限公司將會在台灣成立分公司，將進行家用電視遊樂器之販售及物料供應安排業務。<br />\n<br />\n分公司在 4 月 7 日正式成立，公司董事為後藤正志，資本總額為 500 萬新台幣。這些資訊都與台灣經濟部商業司上找到的詳情一致。雖然任天堂曾在 2014 年把台灣市場業務轉交任天堂香港負責，但現在再回台設立分公司，相信是打算對 Nitntendo Switch 目前在台灣市場的進一步拓展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1-10-549x580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1-10-549x580.jpg&h=d0be0e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當 Nitntendo Switch 在台灣設立分公司意味著台灣玩家需要從當地的 Nintendo eShop 中購買遊戲，價錢和遊戲數量也會受到相應影響。現時台灣玩家大多從日本、美國及香港的Nintendo eShop 購入數位版的Switch遊戲，若然台灣分公司成立，有玩家擔心會大大限制了從外地跨區購買遊戲的選擇，價錢也會比其他地區高。有網民紛紛留言表達憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n過去任天堂曾在台灣開設過任天堂的子公司，但卻在 2014 年時結束營業並把重心轉交到香港。現時又重回台灣開分公司，令人猜測是否參考 SONY 撤離香港的做法。"},{"pid":"a744f1e0d64fe5e1a757783e8f0cb2e0db2b7b1b","tid":2488923,"uid":19642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"唉 要變孤兒仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf98786a2adbd8208d169a7db0e1e2bccb7caf4","tid":2488923,"uid":522,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"將香港地區併入埋大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d951a762ad8a899e079d3b19efb803aa4a1c2ddd","tid":2488923,"uid":381591,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"不如你讀一次間公司叫咩名先出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nApple來港開分公司，恐撤離美國"},{"pid":"4ad97e6082c3f082456680af0b3da1a0b1309feb","tid":2488923,"uid":393730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"好快只有台灣行貨<br />\n無港版行貨"},{"pid":"7d131c1be06baeb12ba88307901f96fe9f7a066b","tid":2488923,"uid":386830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"連人哋公司名都打錯係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申前新聞從業員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd1284538ccb6c1f9542e666e06890e7f7ed993","tid":2488923,"uid":2902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"最好換埋香港代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7523ee530dbee4f4c904ed68f298e0c91535f0f","tid":2488923,"uid":394645,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"老任唔喺好想打入中國市場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩呢家唔入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明早幾年好進取架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0167df7998b63710329a3ba62d69f1101bfca85c","tid":2488923,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7523ee530dbee4f4c904ed68f298e0c91535f0f","tid":2488923,"uid":394645,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"老任唔喺好想打入中國市場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩呢家唔入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明早幾年好進取架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj